# Test Discipline

## Must
- Add or update tests for changed behavior in at least one relevant class:
  - unit,
  - integration,
  - property/fuzz for parser/serialization and boundary-heavy logic,
  - determinism replay when simulation state paths are touched.
- Keep canonical scenario coverage aligned with `S1`, `S2`, `S3` for benchmarked paths.
- Attach test pass/fail outputs to CI artifacts.

## Must Not
- Do not merge logic changes with no test delta and no explicit no-test justification.
- Do not treat benchmark outputs as substitutes for unit/integration tests.

## Required Evidence
- Test matrix snippet listing updated suites and why they are sufficient.
